    <div class="maincontent"> 
     <div class="eleven columns"> 
      <p>RIT is home to more than 50 interdisciplinary research centers, institutes, and organizations that bring together faculty and students from across the university. These entities explore a wide range of topics and cover everything from business and entrepreneurship to biomedical sciences, nanolithography, printing, social computing, remanufacturing, Microsystems fabrication, environmental sustainability, and visual perception.</p> 
     </div> 
